"use strict";(self["webpackChunktome_planner"]=self["webpackChunktome_planner"]||[]).push([[873],{10873:function(e){e.exports=JSON.parse('[{"__ATOMIC":true,"allow_random":true,"category":"cunning","description":"Using darkness and a bit of magic, you manipulate the shadows.","is_spell":true,"min_lev":10,"name":"ambush","no_silence":true,"points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"cooldown":15,"id":"T_SHADOWGUARD","image":"shadowguard.png","info_text":"<p>Your Soothing Darkness talent effect now grants 25% all damage resistance on exiting stealth.</p><p>When your life drops below 50% you become immune to negative detrimental effects for 2 turns and gain <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>spellpower 100\\">49, 67, 81, 93, 103</acronym> defense and <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>spellpower 100\\">49, 67, 81, 93, 103</acronym> spellpower for 5 turns.</p>","is_spell":true,"mode":"passive","multi_require":true,"name":"Shadowguard","no_silence":true,"points":5,"require":["Level 10, Cun 22","Level 11, Cun 24","Level 12, Cun 26","Level 13, Cun 28","Level 14, Cun 30"],"short_name":"SHADOWGUARD","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/ambush.lua",22],"type":["cunning/ambush",1]},{"cooldown":20,"cost":"30 mana, 15 stamina","id":"T_SHADOW_GRASP","image":"shadow_ambush.png","info_text":"<p>You reach out with the shadows silencing and disarming your target for 3 turns.</p><p>The shadows will deal <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>spellpower 100\\">343, 467, 563, 645, 717</acronym> darkness damage to the target and pull it to you.</p><p>The chance to apply debuffs improves with your Accuracy and the damage with your Spellpower.</p>","is_spell":true,"mana":30,"mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Shadow Grasp","no_break_stealth":true,"no_silence":true,"points":5,"range":"10.0","require":["Level 14, Cun 30","Level 15, Cun 32","Level 16, Cun 34","Level 17, Cun 36","Level 18, Cun 38"],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"SHADOW_GRASP","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/ambush.lua",52],"speed":"spell","stamina":15,"type":["cunning/ambush",2],"use_speed":"Spell"},{"id":"T_UMBRAL_AGILITY","image":"ambuscade.png","info_text":"<p>Your mastery of dark magic empowers you.</p><p>You gain <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>spellpower 100\\">34, 47, 57, 65, 73</acronym> Accuracy, <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>spellpower 100\\">34, 47, 57, 65, 73</acronym> Defense, and <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>spellpower 100\\">27%, 37%, 45%, 52%, 57%</acronym> Darkness damage penetration.</p><p>The effects will increase with your Spellpower stat.</p>","is_spell":true,"mode":"passive","multi_require":true,"name":"Umbral Agility","no_silence":true,"points":5,"require":["Level 18, Cun 38","Level 19, Cun 40","Level 20, Cun 42","Level 21, Cun 44","Level 22, Cun 46"],"short_name":"UMBRAL_AGILITY","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/ambush.lua",111],"type":["cunning/ambush",3]},{"cooldown":15,"cost":"60 mana, 30 stamina","id":"T_SHADOW_VEIL","image":"shadow_veil.png","info_text":"<p>You veil yourself in shadows and let them control you.</p><p>Immediately after activation and each turn for 3 turns, you blink to a nearby foe (within range 7 of the location of the first target hit), hitting it for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">152%, 178%, 197%, 214%, 229%</acronym> darkness weapon damage.</p><p>While veiled, you become immune to status effects and gain <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>spellpower 100\\">31%, 42%, 51%, 58%, 65%</acronym> all resistance.</p><p>While this goes on, you cannot be stopped unless you are killed, and you cannot control your character.</p><p>If a target isn\'t found this effect ends.</p><p>The movement is not considered a teleport.</p><p>The resistance will increase with your Spellpower stat.</p>","is_spell":true,"mana":60,"mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Shadow Veil","no_silence":true,"points":5,"range":"7.0","require":["Level 22, Cun 46","Level 23, Cun 48","Level 24, Cun 50","Level 25, Cun 52","Level 26, Cun 54"],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"SHADOW_VEIL","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/ambush.lua",132],"speed":"spell","stamina":30,"type":["cunning/ambush",4],"use_speed":"Spell"}],"type":"cunning/ambush"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"allow_random":true,"category":"cunning","description":"Create and use cunning tools.","min_lev":10,"name":"artifice","points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"cooldown":10,"cost":"0 stamina","id":"T_ROGUE_S_TOOLS","image":"rogue_s_tools.png","info_text":"<p>With some advanced preparation, you learn to create and equip one of a number of useful tools (at <span style=\\"color: #ffff00\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-YELLOW\\">level <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 2, 3, 4, 5</acronym><span style=\\"color: #ffffff\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-WHITE\\">):</p><p></p><p>Grappling Hook:</p><p>Throw a grappling hook up to range <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">4, 5, 6, 7, 8</acronym> that drags you towards the target or the target towards you. 8 turn cooldown.</p><p></p><p>Rogue\'s Brew:</p><p>Prepare a potion that restores <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">253, 328, 392, 450, 503</acronym> life, <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">63, 81, 98, 113, 127</acronym> stamina, and cures <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 2, 2, 3, 3</acronym> negative physical effects. 20 turn cooldown.</p><p></p><p>Dart Launcher:</p><p>Fire a poisoned dart dealing <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">77, 96, 110, 122, 133</acronym> physical damage that puts the target to sleep for 4 turns. 10 turn cooldown.</p><p></p><p>Smokescreen:</p><p>Throw a smokebomb creating a radius 2 cloud of smoke, lasting <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">4, 5, 5, 6, 6</acronym> turns, that blocks sight and reduces enemies\' vision by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 4, 5, 7, 8.</acronym> 15 turn cooldown.</p><p></p><p>Hidden Blades:</p><p>Melee criticals trigger an extra unarmed attack, inflicting <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">145%, 164%, 178%, 190%, 201%</acronym> damage. 4 turn cooldown.</p><p></p><p>Preparing a tool sets its talent level and puts it on cooldown.</p><p></p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Rogue\'s Tools","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":5,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 10, Cun 22","Level 11, Cun 24","Level 12, Cun 26","Level 13, Cun 28","Level 14, Cun 30"],"short_name":"ROGUE_S_TOOLS","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/artifice.lua",112],"stamina":0,"type":["cunning/artifice",1],"use_speed":"Standard"},{"cooldown":10,"cost":"0 stamina","id":"T_CUNNING_TOOLS","image":"cunning_tools.png","info_text":"<p>With some advanced preparation, you learn to create and equip a second tool (at <span style=\\"color: #ffff00\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-YELLOW\\">level <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 2, 3, 4, 5</acronym><span style=\\"color: #ffffff\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-WHITE\\">):</p><p></p><p>Grappling Hook:</p><p>Throw a grappling hook up to range <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">4, 5, 6, 7, 8</acronym> that drags you towards the target or the target towards you. 8 turn cooldown.</p><p></p><p>Rogue\'s Brew:</p><p>Prepare a potion that restores <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">253, 328, 392, 450, 503</acronym> life, <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">63, 81, 98, 113, 127</acronym> stamina, and cures <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 2, 2, 3, 3</acronym> negative physical effects. 20 turn cooldown.</p><p></p><p>Dart Launcher:</p><p>Fire a poisoned dart dealing <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">77, 96, 110, 122, 133</acronym> physical damage that puts the target to sleep for 4 turns. 10 turn cooldown.</p><p></p><p>Smokescreen:</p><p>Throw a smokebomb creating a radius 2 cloud of smoke, lasting <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">4, 5, 5, 6, 6</acronym> turns, that blocks sight and reduces enemies\' vision by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 4, 5, 7, 8.</acronym> 15 turn cooldown.</p><p></p><p>Hidden Blades:</p><p>Melee criticals trigger an extra unarmed attack, inflicting <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">145%, 164%, 178%, 190%, 201%</acronym> damage. 4 turn cooldown.</p><p></p><p>Preparing a tool sets its talent level and puts it on cooldown.</p><p>Only one tool of each type can be equipped at a time.</p><p></p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Cunning Tools","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":5,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 14, Cun 30","Level 15, Cun 32","Level 16, Cun 34","Level 17, Cun 36","Level 18, Cun 38"],"short_name":"CUNNING_TOOLS","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/artifice.lua",150],"stamina":0,"type":["cunning/artifice",2],"use_speed":"Standard"},{"cooldown":10,"cost":"0 stamina","id":"T_INTRICATE_TOOLS","image":"intricate_tools.png","info_text":"<p>With some advanced preparation, you learn to create and equip a third tool (at <span style=\\"color: #ffff00\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-YELLOW\\">level <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 2, 3, 4, 5</acronym><span style=\\"color: #ffffff\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-WHITE\\">):</p><p></p><p>Grappling Hook:</p><p>Throw a grappling hook up to range <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">4, 5, 6, 7, 8</acronym> that drags you towards the target or the target towards you. 8 turn cooldown.</p><p></p><p>Rogue\'s Brew:</p><p>Prepare a potion that restores <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">253, 328, 392, 450, 503</acronym> life, <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">63, 81, 98, 113, 127</acronym> stamina, and cures <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 2, 2, 3, 3</acronym> negative physical effects. 20 turn cooldown.</p><p></p><p>Dart Launcher:</p><p>Fire a poisoned dart dealing <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">77, 96, 110, 122, 133</acronym> physical damage that puts the target to sleep for 4 turns. 10 turn cooldown.</p><p></p><p>Smokescreen:</p><p>Throw a smokebomb creating a radius 2 cloud of smoke, lasting <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">4, 5, 5, 6, 6</acronym> turns, that blocks sight and reduces enemies\' vision by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 4, 5, 7, 8.</acronym> 15 turn cooldown.</p><p></p><p>Hidden Blades:</p><p>Melee criticals trigger an extra unarmed attack, inflicting <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">145%, 164%, 178%, 190%, 201%</acronym> damage. 4 turn cooldown.</p><p></p><p>Preparing a tool sets its talent level and puts it on cooldown.</p><p>Only one tool of each type can be equipped at a time.</p><p></p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Intricate Tools","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":5,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 18, Cun 38","Level 19, Cun 40","Level 20, Cun 42","Level 21, Cun 44","Level 22, Cun 46"],"short_name":"INTRICATE_TOOLS","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/artifice.lua",183],"stamina":0,"type":["cunning/artifice",3],"use_speed":"Standard"},{"cooldown":10,"cost":"0 stamina","id":"T_MASTER_ARTIFICER","image":"master_artificer.png","info_text":"<p>You become a master of your craft, allowing you to focus on a single tool (<span style=\\"color: #ffff00\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-YELLOW\\">currently none</span></span>) to greatly improve its capabilities:</p><p></p><p>Grappling Hook (Grappling Hook Mastery)</p><p>Your grappling hook deals 100% unarmed damage when it hits, plus a further <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">110, 135, 154, 169, 182</acronym> physical and <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">110, 135, 154, 169, 182</acronym> nature damage over 4 turns.</p><p></p><p>Rogue\'s Brew (Rogue\'s Brew Mastery)</p><p>Your Rogue\'s Brew fortifies you for 8 turns, preventing you from dying until you reach <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">-207, -419, -581, -718, -839</acronym> life.</p><p></p><p>Dart Launcher (Dart Launcher Mastery)</p><p>Your darts ignore poison and sleep immunity and waking targets are slowed by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">22%, 31%, 36%, 39%, 41%</acronym> for 4 turns.</p><p></p><p>Smokescreen (Smokescreen Mastery)</p><p>Your Smokescreen is infused with chokedust. Enemies in the smoke take <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">92, 111, 125, 137, 148</acronym> nature damage and may be silenced.</p><p></p><p>Hidden Blades (Assassinate)</p><p>You prime your Hidden Blades to cause bleeding and facilitate the Assassinate ability, which allows you to strike twice for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">247%, 276%, 297%, 315%, 331%</acronym> unarmed damage, hitting automatically while ignoring armor and resistance.</p><p></p><p>The effects depend on this talent\'s level.</p><p>Mastering a new tool places it (and its special effects, as appropriate) on cooldown.</p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Master Artificer","no_energy":true,"no_unlearn_last":true,"points":5,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 22, Cun 46","Level 23, Cun 48","Level 24, Cun 50","Level 25, Cun 52","Level 26, Cun 54"],"short_name":"MASTER_ARTIFICER","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/artifice.lua",216],"stamina":0,"type":["cunning/artifice",4],"use_speed":"Instant"}],"type":"cunning/artifice"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"allow_random":true,"category":"cunning","description":"Inflict maximum pain to specific places on your enemies.","name":"Called Shots","points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"archery_target_parameters":{"limit_shots":1,"multishots":1},"cooldown":"8","cost":"10 stamina","id":"T_SKIRMISHER_KNEECAPPER","image":"skirmisher_kneecapper.png","info_text":"<p>Strike your opponent in the knee (or other critical point in an ambulatory appendage) for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">172%, 181%, 189%, 195%, 200%</acronym> weapon damage, knocking them down (<acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 1, 1, 2, 2</acronym> turn pin) and slowing their movement by <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">43%, 47%, 49%, 51%, 53%</acronym> for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">3, 4, 4, 5, 5</acronym> turns afterwards.</p><p>This shot will bypass other enemies between you and your target.</p><p>The slow effect becomes more powerful with your Cunning.</p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Kneecapper","no_energy":"fake","points":5,"random_ego":"attack","range":"archery","require":["Level 0, Cun 12","Level 1, Cun 14","Level 2, Cun 16","Level 3, Cun 18","Level 4, Cun 20"],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"SKIRMISHER_KNEECAPPER","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/called-shots.lua",69],"speed":"archery","stamina":10,"type":["cunning/called-shots",1],"use_speed":"Archery"},{"archery_target_parameters":{"limit_shots":1,"multishots":1},"cooldown":"8","cost":"35 stamina","id":"T_SKIRMISHER_THROAT_SMASHER","image":"skirmisher_throat_smasher.png","info_text":"<p>Employ a specialized sniping shot at a target.</p><p>This shot is focused on precision at long range and deals base <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">97%, 126%, 147%, 165%, 181%</acronym> ranged damage with a bonus that increases with distance.</p><p>The ranged bonus is -49% (penalty) at point blank range, while at your maximum range of 10 it is 250%.</p><p>This shot will bypass other enemies between you and your target.</p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Kill Shot","no_energy":"fake","points":5,"random_ego":"attack","range":"archery","require":["Level 4, Cun 20","Level 5, Cun 22","Level 6, Cun 24","Level 7, Cun 26","Level 8, Cun 28"],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"SKIRMISHER_THROAT_SMASHER","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/called-shots.lua",123],"speed":"archery","stamina":35,"type":["cunning/called-shots",2],"use_speed":"Archery"},{"archery_target_parameters":{"limit_shots":1,"multishots":3},"cooldown":"8","cost":"15 stamina","id":"T_SKIRMISHER_NOGGIN_KNOCKER","image":"skirmisher_noggin_knocker.png","info_text":"<p>Fire three shots in quick succession at a vulnerable point on the target (usually the head).</p><p>Each shot deals <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">55%, 66%, 74%, 80%, 86%</acronym> Ranged damage and will try to stun or increase the target\'s stun duration by 1.</p><p>These shots will bypass other enemies between you and your target.</p><p>The chance to stun increases with your Accuracy.</p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Noggin Knocker","no_energy":"fake","points":5,"range":"archery","require":["Level 8, Cun 28","Level 9, Cun 30","Level 10, Cun 32","Level 11, Cun 34","Level 12, Cun 36"],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"SKIRMISHER_NOGGIN_KNOCKER","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/called-shots.lua",188],"speed":"archery","stamina":15,"type":["cunning/called-shots",3],"use_speed":"Archery"},{"id":"T_SKIRMISHER_SLING_SNIPER","image":"skirmisher_sling_sniper.png","info_text":"<p>Your mastery of called shots is unparalleled. and you gain <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">4%, 7%, 9%, 11%, 13%</acronym> bonus critical chance and <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">11%, 15%, 19%, 22%, 26%</acronym> critical damage with your Called Shots Talents. At rank 3 the cooldowns of all of your Called Shots Talents are reduced by 2 each. At rank 5 you gain <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">15%, 24%, 35%, 43%, 49%</acronym> Physical resistance penetration with all Called Shot attacks.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":true,"name":"Sling Sniper","no_energy":"fake","points":5,"require":["Level 12, Cun 36","Level 13, Cun 38","Level 14, Cun 40","Level 15, Cun 42","Level 16, Cun 44"],"short_name":"SKIRMISHER_SLING_SNIPER","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/called-shots.lua",226],"type":["cunning/called-shots",4]}],"type":"cunning/called-shots"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"allow_random":true,"category":"cunning","description":"Teaches various talents to cripple your foes.","name":"dirty fighting","points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"cooldown":10,"cost":"12 stamina","id":"T_DIRTY_FIGHTING","image":"dirty_fighting.png","info_text":"<p>You make a low blow against a sensitive point on the target, dealing <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">183%, 198%, 208%, 217%, 225%</acronym> unarmed damage. If your attack hits, the target is left reeling and vulnerable, reducing their physical save by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">9, 17, 24, 29, 34</acronym> and their stun, blind, confusion and pin immunities to 50% of normal for 4 turns.</p><p>This effect bypasses saves.</p>","is_melee":true,"mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Dirty Fighting","points":5,"random_ego":"attack","range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 0, Cun 12","Level 1, Cun 14","Level 2, Cun 16","Level 3, Cun 18","Level 4, Cun 20"],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"DIRTY_FIGHTING","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/dirty.lua",22],"speed":"weapon","stamina":12,"type":["cunning/dirty",1],"use_speed":"Weapon"},{"id":"T_BACKSTAB","image":"backstab.png","info_text":"<p>Your quick wit gives you a big advantage against disabled targets, increasing your damage by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">5%, 7%, 9%, 11%, 12%</acronym> for each disabling effect the target is under, to a maximum of <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">15%, 23%, 29%, 34%, 38%.</acronym></p><p>For this purpose, disabling effects are stun, blind, daze, confuse, pin, disarm, cripple and silence.</p><p>In addition, for each disabling effect the target is under, your melee attacks have a <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">2%, 4%, 6%, 7%, 8%</acronym> (to a maximum of <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">8%, 14%, 18%, 22%, 25%</acronym>) chance to inflict a new effect on them (that they do not already have): either disarm, cripple (25% power) or pin for 2 turns.</p><p>The chance to further disable the target increases with your Accuracy.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":true,"name":"Backstab","points":5,"require":["Level 4, Cun 20","Level 5, Cun 22","Level 6, Cun 24","Level 7, Cun 26","Level 8, Cun 28"],"short_name":"BACKSTAB","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/dirty.lua",61],"type":["cunning/dirty",2]},{"cooldown":12,"cost":"18 stamina","direct_hit":true,"id":"T_BLINDING_POWDER","image":"blinding_powder.png","info_text":"<p>Throw a cloud of blinding dust in a radius <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 1, 2, 2, 3</acronym> cone. Enemies within will be blinded, as well as having their accuracy reduced by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">11, 18, 24, 29, 34</acronym> and movement speed decreased by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">39%, 55%, 64%, 69%, 73%</acronym> for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">3, 4, 4, 5, 5</acronym> turns.</p><p>The chance to inflict these effects increase with your Accuracy.</p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Blinding Powder","points":5,"random_ego":"attack","range":"0.0","require":["Level 8, Cun 28","Level 9, Cun 30","Level 10, Cun 32","Level 11, Cun 34","Level 12, Cun 36"],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"BLINDING_POWDER","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/dirty.lua",113],"stamina":18,"type":["cunning/dirty",3],"use_speed":"Standard"},{"cooldown":15,"cost":"20 stamina","fixed_cooldown":true,"id":"T_TWIST_THE_KNIFE","image":"twist_the_knife.png","info_text":"<p>Make a painful strike dealing <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">128%, 140%, 148%, 156%, 163%</acronym> weapon damage that increases the duration of up to <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 2, 2, 3, 3</acronym> negative effect(s) on the target by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">2, 3, 4, 5, 6</acronym> turns. For each negative effect extended this way, the duration of a beneficial effect is reduced by the same amount, possibly canceling it.</p>","is_melee":true,"mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Twist the Knife","points":5,"random_ego":"attack","range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 12, Cun 36","Level 13, Cun 38","Level 14, Cun 40","Level 15, Cun 42","Level 16, Cun 44"],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"TWIST_THE_KNIFE","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/dirty.lua",150],"speed":"weapon","stamina":20,"type":["cunning/dirty",4],"use_speed":"Weapon"}],"type":"cunning/dirty"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"allow_random":true,"category":"cunning","description":"How to make your foes feel the pain.","generic":true,"name":"lethality","points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"generic":true,"id":"T_LETHALITY","image":"lethality.png","info_text":"<p>You have learned to find and hit weak spots. All your strikes have a <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">3.7%, 6.0%, 7.4%, 8.4%, 9.2%</acronym> greater chance to be critical hits, and your critical hits do <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">11%, 16%, 20%, 22%, 24%</acronym> more damage.</p><p>Also, when using knives and throwing knives, you now use your Cunning instead of your Strength for bonus damage.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":true,"name":"Lethality","points":5,"require":["Level 0, Cun 12","Level 1, Cun 14","Level 2, Cun 16","Level 3, Cun 18","Level 4, Cun 20"],"short_name":"LETHALITY","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/lethality.lua",20],"type":["cunning/lethality",1]},{"cooldown":6,"cost":"20 stamina","generic":true,"id":"T_EXPOSE_WEAKNESS","image":"expose_weakness.png","info_text":"<p>Focus on a single target and perform a probing attack to find flaws in its defences, striking with your melee weapon(s) for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">96%, 104%, 109%, 113%, 117%</acronym> damage.</p><p>For 3 turns thereafter, you gain <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">25, 33, 39, 44, 48</acronym> armor penetration, <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">38, 49, 58, 66, 73</acronym> accuracy, and 30% all damage peneration.</p><p>Learning this technique allows you to permanently gain <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">5, 7, 9, 11, 13</acronym> armour penetration with all melee and archery attacks.</p><p>The temporary armor penetration and accuracy bonuses increase with Cunning.</p>","is_melee":true,"mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Expose Weakness","points":5,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 4, Cun 20","Level 5, Cun 22","Level 6, Cun 24","Level 7, Cun 26","Level 8, Cun 28"],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"EXPOSE_WEAKNESS","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/lethality.lua",41],"stamina":20,"type":["cunning/lethality",2],"use_speed":"Weapon"},{"cooldown":30,"cost":"30 stamina","deactivate_on":{"no_combat":true,"rest":true,"run":true},"drain_stamina":4,"generic":true,"id":"T_BLADE_FLURRY","image":"blade_flurry.png","info_text":"<p>Become a whirling storm of blades, increasing attack speed by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">14%, 22%, 29%, 34%, 39%</acronym> and causing melee attacks to strike an additional adjacent target other than your primary target for 100% weapon damage. </p><p>This talent is exhausting to use, draining 4 stamina each turn.</p>","mode":"sustained","multi_require":true,"name":"Blade Flurry","no_break_stealth":true,"no_energy":true,"points":5,"range":"melee/personal","remove_on_zero":true,"require":["Level 8, Cun 28","Level 9, Cun 30","Level 10, Cun 32","Level 11, Cun 34","Level 12, Cun 36"],"short_name":"BLADE_FLURRY","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/lethality.lua",86],"sustain_stamina":30,"type":["cunning/lethality",3],"use_speed":"Instant"},{"cooldown":30,"cost":"25 stamina","fixed_cooldown":true,"generic":true,"id":"T_SNAP","image":"snap.png","info_text":"<p>Your quick wits allow you to reset the cooldown of up to <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">3, 5, 6, 7, 8</acronym> of your combat talents (cunning or technique) of tier <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 2, 3, 4, 5</acronym> or less.</p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Snap","points":5,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 12, Cun 36","Level 13, Cun 38","Level 14, Cun 40","Level 15, Cun 42","Level 16, Cun 44"],"short_name":"SNAP","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/lethality.lua",143],"speed":"combat","stamina":25,"type":["cunning/lethality",4],"use_speed":"Combat"}],"type":"cunning/lethality"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"allow_random":true,"category":"cunning","description":"Collection of known poisons.","name":"poisons","points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"cooldown":10,"id":"T_NUMBING_POISON","image":"numbing_poison.png","info_text":"<p>Enhances your Deadly Poison with a numbing agent, causing the poison to reduce all damage the target deals by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Vile Poisons talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">16%, 20%, 23%, 24%, 26%.</acronym></p>","mode":"sustained","name":"Numbing Poison","no_break_stealth":true,"no_energy":true,"no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"poison_tactics":{"defend":{"poison":-0.5},"disable":{"poison":1.5}},"range":"melee/personal","short_name":"NUMBING_POISON","source_code":["",402],"type":["cunning/poisons-effects",1],"use_speed":"Instant"},{"cooldown":10,"id":"T_INSIDIOUS_POISON","image":"insidious_poison.png","info_text":"<p>Enhances your Deadly Poison with an insidious agent, causing it to reduce the healing taken by enemies by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Vile Poisons talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">52%, 62%, 69%, 74%, 79%.</acronym></p>","mode":"sustained","name":"Insidious Poison","no_break_stealth":true,"no_energy":true,"no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"poison_tactics":{"attack":{"poison":1.5},"disable":{"poison":0.5}},"range":"melee/personal","short_name":"INSIDIOUS_POISON","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/poisons.lua",434],"type":["cunning/poisons-effects",1],"use_speed":"Instant"},{"cooldown":10,"id":"T_CRIPPLING_POISON","image":"crippling_poison.png","info_text":"<p>Enhances your Deadly Poison with a crippling agent, giving enemies a <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Vile Poisons talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">16%, 20%, 23%, 24%, 26%</acronym> chance on using a talent to fail and lose a turn.</p>","mode":"sustained","name":"Crippling Poison","no_break_stealth":true,"no_energy":true,"no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"poison_tactics":{"disable":{"poison":2}},"range":"melee/personal","short_name":"CRIPPLING_POISON","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/poisons.lua",466],"type":["cunning/poisons-effects",1],"use_speed":"Instant"},{"cooldown":10,"id":"T_LEECHING_POISON","image":"leeching_poison.png","info_text":"<p>Enhances your Deadly Poison with a leeching agent, causing it to heal you for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Vile Poisons talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">20%, 28%, 35%, 39%, 43%</acronym> of the damage it does to its target.</p>","mode":"sustained","name":"Leeching Poison","no_break_stealth":true,"no_energy":true,"no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"poison_tactics":{"heal":{"poison":-2}},"range":"melee/personal","short_name":"LEECHING_POISON","source_code":["",498],"type":["cunning/poisons-effects",1],"use_speed":"Instant"},{"cooldown":10,"id":"T_VOLATILE_POISON","image":"volatile_poison.png","info_text":"<p>Enhances your Deadly Poison with a volatile agent, causing the poison to deal <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Vile Poisons talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">25%, 36%, 44%, 49%, 54%</acronym> increased damage to the victim and damage all of your enemies adjacent to it for 50%.</p>","mode":"sustained","name":"Volatile Poison","no_break_stealth":true,"no_energy":true,"no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"poison_tactics":{"attackarea":{"NATURE":1}},"range":"melee/personal","short_name":"VOLATILE_POISON","source_code":["",530],"type":["cunning/poisons-effects",1],"use_speed":"Instant"},{"id":"T_VULNERABILITY_POISON","image":"vulnerability_poison.png","info_text":"<p>Whenever you apply Deadly Poison, you also apply an unresistable magical poison dealing <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Magic 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">20, 26, 35, 43, 50</acronym> arcane damage (based on your Magic) each turn. This poison reduces all damage resistance by 10% and poison immunity by 50%.</p>","mode":"passive","name":"Vulnerability Poison","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"short_name":"VULNERABILITY_POISON","source_code":["",568],"type":["cunning/poisons-effects",1]},{"cooldown":10,"id":"T_STONING_POISON","image":"stoning_poison.png","info_text":"<p>Enhance your Deadly Poison with a stoning agent.  Whenever you apply Deadly Poison, you afflict your target with an additional earth-based poison that inflicts <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Vile Poisons talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">13, 15, 16, 17, 18</acronym> nature damage per turn (stacking up to <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Vile Poisons talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">54, 61, 67, 71, 75</acronym> damage per turn) for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Vile Poisons talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">6, 7, 7, 8, 8</acronym> turns.</p><p>After either <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Vile Poisons talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">7, 4, 3, 3, 2</acronym> turns or the poison has run its course (&lt;100% chance, see effect description), the target will be turned to stone for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Vile Poisons talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">3, 3, 3, 4, 4</acronym> turns.</p><p>The damage scales with your Cunning.</p>","mode":"sustained","multi_require":false,"name":"Stoning Poison","no_break_stealth":true,"no_energy":true,"no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 25, Cun 40"],"short_name":"STONING_POISON","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/poisons.lua",582],"type":["cunning/poisons-effects",1],"type_no_req":true,"use_speed":"Instant","vile_poison":true}],"type":"cunning/poisons-effects"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"allow_random":true,"category":"cunning","description":"The knowledge of poisons and how to apply them to \'good\' effects.","name":"poisons","points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"cooldown":10,"cost":"10 stamina","id":"T_APPLY_POISON","image":"apply_poison.png","info_text":"<p>Learn how to coat your melee weapons, throwing knives, sling and bow ammo with poison, giving your attacks a <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">32%, 40%, 45%, 49%, 53%</acronym> chance to poison the target for <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">24, 29, 32, 36, 38</acronym> nature damage per turn for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">4, 5, 6, 7, 8</acronym> turns. Every application of the poison stacks, up to a maximum of <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">96, 116, 131, 144, 154</acronym> nature damage per turn.</p><p>The damage scales with your Cunning.</p>","mode":"sustained","multi_require":true,"name":"Apply Poison","no_break_stealth":true,"points":5,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 0, Cun 12","Level 1, Cun 14","Level 2, Cun 16","Level 3, Cun 18","Level 4, Cun 20"],"short_name":"APPLY_POISON","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/poisons.lua",119],"sustain_stamina":10,"type":["cunning/poisons",1],"use_speed":"Standard"},{"id":"T_TOXIC_DEATH","image":"toxic_death.png","info_text":"<p>When you kill a creature, all of your poisons affecting it will spread to foes in a radius of <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">2, 3, 4, 4, 5.</acronym></p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":true,"name":"Toxic Death","points":5,"require":["Level 4, Cun 20","Level 5, Cun 22","Level 6, Cun 24","Level 7, Cun 26","Level 8, Cun 28"],"short_name":"TOXIC_DEATH","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/poisons.lua",193],"type":["cunning/poisons",2]},{"id":"T_VILE_POISONS","image":"vile_poisons.png","info_text":"<p>Learn how to enhance your Deadly Poison, adding additional effects. Each level, you will learn a new kind of poison enhancement:</p><ul><li>Level 1: Numbing Poison</li><li>Level 2: Insidious Poison</li><li>Level 3: Crippling Poison</li><li>Level 4: Leeching Poison</li><li>Level 5: Volatile Poison</li></ul><p>New poison enhancements can also be learned from special teachers in the world.</p><p>Also increases the effectiveness of your poisons by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">32%, 64%, 96%, 128%, 160%.</acronym> (The effect varies for each poison.)</p><p>Adjusting your weapon coating takes no time and does not break stealth.</p><p>You may only have two poison enhancements active at once; applying a third will randomly cause one of the existing ones to be cancelled.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":true,"name":"Vile Poisons","points":5,"require":["Level 8, Cun 28","Level 9, Cun 30","Level 10, Cun 32","Level 11, Cun 34","Level 12, Cun 36"],"short_name":"VILE_POISONS","source_code":["",238],"type":["cunning/poisons",3]},{"cooldown":10,"cost":"14 stamina","id":"T_VENOMOUS_STRIKE","image":"venomous_strike.png","info_text":"<p>You strike your target with your melee or ranged weapon, doing <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">170%, 192%, 208%, 221%, 233%</acronym> weapon damage as nature and inflicting additional effects based on your active vile poisons:</p><p></p><p>Numbing Poison - Reduces global speed by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">21%, 28%, 32%, 34%, 36%</acronym> for 5 turns.</p><p>Insidious Poison - Applies a standard poison that deals <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">200, 261, 306, 344, 376</acronym> nature damage over 5 turns.</p><p>Crippling Poison - Places <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 3, 3, 4, 4</acronym> talents on cooldown for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 4, 4, 6, 6</acronym> turns.</p><p>Leeching Poison - Heals you for <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">199, 260, 305, 343, 376.</acronym></p><p>Volatile Poison - Deals a further <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">120, 156, 184, 206, 226</acronym> nature damage to foes in a radius <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 3, 3, 4, 4</acronym> ball.</p><p></p><p>Learning this talent in addition to the Throwing Knives talent allows you to learn the Venomous Throw talent, which can be used to throw poisoned daggers at your foes, but is put on cooldown when this talent is used.</p><p></p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Venomous Strike","points":5,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 12, Cun 36","Level 13, Cun 38","Level 14, Cun 40","Level 15, Cun 42","Level 16, Cun 44"],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"VENOMOUS_STRIKE","source_code":["",289],"speed":"weapon","stamina":14,"type":["cunning/poisons",4],"use_speed":"Weapon"}],"type":"cunning/poisons"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"allow_random":true,"category":"cunning","description":"The use of ungentlemanly techniques.","generic":true,"name":"scoundrel","points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"generic":true,"id":"T_LACERATING_STRIKES","image":"lacerating_strikes.png","info_text":"<p>Your melee and ranged attacks have a <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">29%, 42%, 50%, 54%, 57%</acronym> chance to shred enemies inflicting an additional 100% of the damage dealt as a bleed over 4 turns.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":true,"name":"Lacerating Strikes","no_break_stealth":true,"points":5,"require":["Level 0, Cun 12","Level 1, Cun 14","Level 2, Cun 16","Level 3, Cun 18","Level 4, Cun 20"],"short_name":"LACERATING_STRIKES","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/scoundrel.lua",22],"type":["cunning/scoundrel",1]},{"generic":true,"id":"T_SCOUNDREL","image":"scoundrel.png","info_text":"<p>Your melee and ranged attacks inflict distracting wounds that reduce the targetâ€™s critical strike multiplier by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">29%, 43%, 53%, 59%, 64%</acronym> for 5 turns. </p><p>In addition, your attacks have a <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">14%, 23%, 29%, 34%, 38%</acronym> chance to inflict a painful wound that causes them to forget a random talent for 4 turns.  The last effect cannot occur more than once per turn per target.</p><p></p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":true,"name":"Scoundrel\'s Strategies","points":5,"require":["Level 4, Cun 20","Level 5, Cun 22","Level 6, Cun 24","Level 7, Cun 26","Level 8, Cun 28"],"short_name":"SCOUNDREL","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/scoundrel.lua",55],"type":["cunning/scoundrel",2]},{"generic":true,"id":"T_MISDIRECTION","image":"misdirection.png","info_text":"<p>Your abilities in sowing confusion and chaos have reached their peak.  Whenever a foe attempts to apply a detrimental physical effect to you, they have a <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">17%, 26%, 31%, 34%, 37%</acronym> chance to fail. If there is an adjacent enemy to you, you misdirect your foe into applying it to them at <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">32%, 42%, 49%, 54%, 58%</acronym> duration.</p><p>You gain <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">26, 35, 41, 46, 51</acronym> defense.</p><p>The chance to apply status effects increases with your Accuracy and the Defense with your Cunning.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":true,"name":"Misdirection","points":5,"require":["Level 8, Cun 28","Level 9, Cun 30","Level 10, Cun 32","Level 11, Cun 34","Level 12, Cun 36"],"short_name":"MISDIRECTION","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/scoundrel.lua",113],"type":["cunning/scoundrel",3]},{"generic":true,"id":"T_FUMBLE","image":"fumble.png","info_text":"<p>Your melee and ranged attacks leave your foes unable to focus on any complex actions, giving them a stacking 3% chance of failure the next time they try to use a talent (to a maximum of <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">18%, 30%, 39%, 42%, 45%</acronym>).</p><p>If any effect causes the target\'s turn to fail they fumble and injure themself, taking <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">150, 196, 230, 259, 283</acronym> physical damage.</p><p>If the turn loss was caused by this effect then Fumble is removed.</p><p>The damage dealt increases with your Cunning.</p><p></p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":true,"name":"Fumble","points":5,"require":["Level 12, Cun 36","Level 13, Cun 38","Level 14, Cun 40","Level 15, Cun 42","Level 16, Cun 44"],"short_name":"FUMBLE","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/scoundrel.lua",160],"type":["cunning/scoundrel",4]}],"type":"cunning/scoundrel"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"allow_random":true,"category":"cunning","description":"Blending magic and shadows.","is_spell":true,"name":"shadow magic","no_silence":true,"points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"cooldown":5,"cost":"50 mana, 10 stamina","id":"T_SHADOW_COMBAT","image":"shadow_combat.png","info_text":"<p>Channel raw magical energy into your melee attacks; each blow you land will do an additional <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>spellpower 100\\">60, 78, 91, 103, 114</acronym> darkness damage.</p><p>The damage will improve with your Spellpower.</p>","is_spell":true,"mode":"sustained","multi_require":true,"name":"Shadow Combat","no_silence":true,"points":5,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 0, Cun 12","Level 1, Cun 14","Level 2, Cun 16","Level 3, Cun 18","Level 4, Cun 20"],"short_name":"SHADOW_COMBAT","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/shadow-magic.lua",20],"sustain_mana":50,"sustain_stamina":10,"type":["cunning/shadow-magic",1],"use_speed":"Spell"},{"id":"T_SHADOW_CUNNING","image":"shadow_cunning.png","info_text":"<p>Your preparations give you greater magical capabilities. You gain a bonus to Spellpower equal to <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">23%, 31%, 39%, 45%, 52%</acronym> of your Cunning (Current bonus: <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">23, 31, 39, 45, 52</acronym>).</p>","is_spell":true,"mode":"passive","multi_require":true,"name":"Shadow Cunning","no_silence":true,"points":5,"require":["Level 4, Cun 20","Level 5, Cun 22","Level 6, Cun 24","Level 7, Cun 26","Level 8, Cun 28"],"short_name":"SHADOW_CUNNING","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/shadow-magic.lua",58],"type":["cunning/shadow-magic",2]},{"cooldown":5,"cost":"20 mana, 10 stamina","id":"T_SHADOW_FEED","image":"shadow_feed.png","info_text":"<p>You draw energy from the depths of the shadows.</p><p>While sustained, you regenerate <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">0.52, 0.72, 0.85, 0.94, 1.01</acronym> mana per turn, and your physical and spell attack speed increases by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">4.9%, 10%, 15%, 18%, 21%.</acronym></p>","is_spell":true,"mode":"sustained","multi_require":true,"name":"Shadow Feed","no_silence":true,"points":5,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 8, Cun 28","Level 9, Cun 30","Level 10, Cun 32","Level 11, Cun 34","Level 12, Cun 36"],"short_name":"SHADOW_FEED","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/shadow-magic.lua",74],"sustain_mana":20,"sustain_stamina":10,"type":["cunning/shadow-magic",3],"use_speed":"Spell"},{"cooldown":6,"cost":"20 mana, 20 stamina","direct_hit":true,"id":"T_SHADOWSTEP","image":"shadowstep.png","info_text":"<p>Step through the shadows to your target, dazing it for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">3, 4, 5, 5, 5</acronym> turns and hitting it with all your weapons for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">147%, 176%, 197%, 215%, 231%</acronym> darkness weapon damage.</p><p>Dazed targets are significantly impaired, but any damage will free them.</p><p>To Shadowstep, you need to be able to see the target.</p>","is_melee":true,"is_spell":true,"is_teleport":true,"mana":20,"mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Shadowstep","no_silence":true,"points":5,"range":"<acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">6.0, 8.0, 9.0, 10.0, 11.0</acronym>","require":["Level 12, Cun 36","Level 13, Cun 38","Level 14, Cun 40","Level 15, Cun 42","Level 16, Cun 44"],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"SHADOWSTEP","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/shadow-magic.lua",109],"stamina":20,"type":["cunning/shadow-magic",4],"use_speed":"Spell"}],"type":"cunning/shadow-magic"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"allow_random":true,"category":"cunning","description":"Allows the user to enter stealth.","name":"stealth","points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"allow_autocast":true,"cooldown":10,"id":"T_STEALTH","image":"stealth.png","info_text":"<p>Enters stealth mode (power <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">45, 56, 64, 69, 74,</acronym> based on Cunning), making you harder to detect.</p><p>If successful (re-checked each turn), enemies will not know exactly where you are, or may not notice you at all.</p><p>Stealth reduces your light radius to 0, increases your infravision by 3, and will not work with heavy or massive armours.</p><p>You cannot enter stealth if there are foes in sight within range <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">8, 7, 5, 5, 4.</acronym></p><p>Any non-instant, non-movement action will break stealth if not otherwise specified.</p><p></p><p>Enemies uncertain of your location will still make educated guesses at it.</p><p>While stealthed, enemies cannot share information about your location with each other and will be delayed in telling their allies that you exist at all.</p>","mode":"sustained","multi_require":true,"name":"Stealth","no_break_stealth":true,"no_energy":true,"no_sustain_autoreset":true,"points":5,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 0, Cun 12","Level 1, Cun 14","Level 2, Cun 16","Level 3, Cun 18","Level 4, Cun 20"],"short_name":"STEALTH","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/stealth.lua",50],"sustain_lists":"break_with_stealth","type":["cunning/stealth",1],"use_speed":"Instant"},{"id":"T_SHADOWSTRIKE","image":"shadowstrike.png","info_text":"<p>You know how to make the most out of being unseen.</p><p>When striking from stealth, your attacks are automatically critical if the target does not notice you just before you land it.  (Spell and mind attacks critically strike even if the target notices you.)</p><p>Your critical multiplier against targets that cannot see you is increased by up to <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">21%, 32%, 39%, 44%, 48%.</acronym> (You must be able to see your target and the bonus is reduced from its full value at range 3 to 0 at range 10.)</p><p>Also, after exiting stealth for any reason, the critical multiplier persists for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">3, 4, 4, 4, 4</acronym> turns (with no range limitation).</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":true,"name":"Shadowstrike","points":5,"require":["Level 4, Cun 20","Level 5, Cun 22","Level 6, Cun 24","Level 7, Cun 26","Level 8, Cun 28"],"short_name":"SHADOWSTRIKE","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/stealth.lua",157],"type":["cunning/stealth",2]},{"id":"T_SOOTHING_DARKNESS","image":"soothing_darkness.png","info_text":"<p>You have a special affinity for darkness and shadows.</p><p>When standing in an unlit grid, the minimum range to your foes for activating stealth or for maintaining it after a Shadow Dance is reduced by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">2, 3, 4, 4, 5.</acronym></p><p>While stealthed, your life regeneration is increased by <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">6.3, 8.2, 9.8, 11, 13</acronym> (based on your Cunning) and your stamina regeneration is increased by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1.3, 2.0, 2.4, 2.9, 3.2.</acronym>  The regeneration effects persist for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">3, 4, 4, 4, 4</acronym> turns after exiting stealth, with 5 times the normal rate.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":true,"name":"Soothing Darkness","points":5,"require":["Level 8, Cun 28","Level 9, Cun 30","Level 10, Cun 32","Level 11, Cun 34","Level 12, Cun 36"],"short_name":"SOOTHING_DARKNESS","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/stealth.lua",179],"type":["cunning/stealth",3]},{"cooldown":"<acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">28, 21, 18, 16, 14</acronym>","cost":"30 stamina","id":"T_SHADOW_DANCE","image":"shadow_dance.png","info_text":"<p>Your mastery of stealth allows you to vanish from sight at any time.</p><p>You automatically enter stealth and cause it to not break from unstealthy actions for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">2, 3, 4, 4, 5</acronym> turns.</p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Shadow Dance","no_break_stealth":true,"no_energy":true,"points":5,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 12, Cun 36","Level 13, Cun 38","Level 14, Cun 40","Level 15, Cun 42","Level 16, Cun 44"],"short_name":"SHADOW_DANCE","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/stealth.lua",200],"stamina":30,"type":["cunning/stealth",4],"use_speed":"Instant"}],"type":"cunning/stealth"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"allow_random":true,"category":"cunning","description":"The knowledge of the dangers of the world, and how to best avoid them.","generic":true,"name":"survival","points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"autolearn_talent":"T_DISARM_TRAP","generic":true,"id":"T_HEIGHTENED_SENSES","image":"heightened_senses.png","info_text":"<p>You notice the small things others do not notice, allowing you to \\"see\\" creatures in a <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">5, 7, 8, 9, 10</acronym> radius even outside of light radius.</p><p>This is not telepathy, however, and it is still limited to line of sight.</p><p>Also, your attention to detail increases stealth detection and invisibility detection by <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">53, 68, 78, 86, 93,</acronym> and you gain the ability to detect traps (<acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">+47, +63, +73, +82, +88</acronym> detect \'power\').</p><p>The detection abilities improve with Cunning.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":true,"name":"Heightened Senses","points":5,"random_boss_rarity":50,"require":["Level 0, Cun 12","Level 1, Cun 14","Level 2, Cun 16","Level 3, Cun 18","Level 4, Cun 20"],"short_name":"HEIGHTENED_SENSES","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/survival.lua",20],"type":["cunning/survival",1]},{"autolearn_talent":"T_DISARM_TRAP","generic":true,"id":"T_DEVICE_MASTERY","image":"device_mastery.png","info_text":"<p>Your cunning manipulations allow you to use charms (wands, totems and torques) more efficiently, reducing their cooldowns and the power cost of all usable items by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">21%, 31%, 39%, 44%, 49%.</acronym></p><p>In addition your knowledge of devices allows you to disarm known traps (<acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">56, 75, 88, 98, 107</acronym> disarm \'power\', improves with Cunning).</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":true,"name":"Device Mastery","points":5,"random_boss_rarity":50,"require":["Level 4, Cun 20","Level 5, Cun 22","Level 6, Cun 24","Level 7, Cun 26","Level 8, Cun 28"],"short_name":"DEVICE_MASTERY","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/survival.lua",51],"type":["cunning/survival",2]},{"cooldown":20,"generic":true,"id":"T_TRACK","image":"track.png","info_text":"<p>Sense foes around you in a radius of <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">21, 27, 33, 37, 41</acronym> for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">4, 6, 7, 8, 9</acronym> turns.</p><p>The radius will increase with your Cunning.</p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Track","no_break_stealth":true,"points":5,"random_ego":"utility","range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 8, Cun 28","Level 9, Cun 30","Level 10, Cun 32","Level 11, Cun 34","Level 12, Cun 36"],"short_name":"TRACK","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/survival.lua",77],"type":["cunning/survival",3],"use_speed":"Standard"},{"generic":true,"id":"T_DANGER_SENSE","image":"danger_sense.png","info_text":"<p>You have an enhanced sense of self preservation, and your keen intuition allows you to sense dangers others miss.</p><p>Your ability to detect traps is enhanced (<acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">+22, +29, +34, +38, +41</acronym> detect \'power\').</p><p>Critical attacks against you have <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">5.3%, 8.9%, 12%, 14%, 16%</acronym> reduced bonus damage, and damage bonuses attackers gain against you for being unseen are reduced by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">19%, 26%, 32%, 36%, 40%.</acronym></p><p>You also gain an additional chance (at your normal save <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">-14, -11, -10, -8, -8,</acronym> effective) to resist detrimental status effects that can be resisted.</p><p>The detection and additional save chance improve with Cunning.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":true,"name":"Danger Sense","points":5,"random_boss_rarity":50,"require":["Level 12, Cun 36","Level 13, Cun 38","Level 14, Cun 40","Level 15, Cun 42","Level 16, Cun 44"],"short_name":"DANGER_SENSE","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/survival.lua",103],"type":["cunning/survival",4]}],"type":"cunning/survival"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"allow_random":true,"category":"cunning","description":"Tactical combat abilities.","name":"tactical","points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"id":"T_TACTICAL_EXPERT","image":"tactical_expert.png","info_text":"<p>Your Defense is increased by <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">5, 7, 10, 12, 15</acronym> for every adjacent visible foe, up to a maximum of <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">+35, +54, +66, +74, +80</acronym> Defense.</p><p>The Defense increase per enemy and maximum Defense bonus will scale with your Cunning.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":true,"name":"Tactical Expert","points":5,"require":["Level 0, Cun 12","Level 1, Cun 14","Level 2, Cun 16","Level 3, Cun 18","Level 4, Cun 20"],"short_name":"TACTICAL_EXPERT","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/tactical.lua",29],"type":["cunning/tactical",1]},{"id":"T_COUNTER_ATTACK","image":"counter_attack.png","info_text":"<p>When you avoid a melee blow from an adjacent foe, you have a <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">25%, 39%, 48%, 56%, 62%</acronym> chance to get a free, automatic melee attack against the attacker for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">72%, 82%, 89%, 95%, 100%</acronym> damage, up to <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">1.0, 1.3, 1.7, 2.0, 2.2</acronym> times per turn.</p><p>Unarmed fighters using it will also attempt to throw the target to the ground if the attack lands, dazing them for 2 turns or stunning them for 2 turns if the target is grappled.</p><p>The chance of countering and number of counter attacks increase with your Cunning.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":true,"name":"Counter Attack","points":5,"require":["Level 4, Cun 20","Level 5, Cun 22","Level 6, Cun 24","Level 7, Cun 26","Level 8, Cun 28"],"short_name":"COUNTER_ATTACK","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/tactical.lua",67],"type":["cunning/tactical",2]},{"cooldown":12,"cost":"12 stamina","id":"T_SET_UP","image":"set_up.png","info_text":"<p>Increases Defense by <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">27, 34, 40, 44, 48</acronym> for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">3, 5, 6, 7, 8</acronym> turns.  When you avoid a melee blow, you set the target up, increasing the chance of you landing a critical strike on them by <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">17%, 20%, 23%, 25%, 28%</acronym> and reducing their saving throws by <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">17, 20, 23, 25, 28.</acronym></p><p>The effects will scale with your Cunning.</p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Set Up","points":5,"random_ego":"utility","range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 8, Cun 28","Level 9, Cun 30","Level 10, Cun 32","Level 11, Cun 34","Level 12, Cun 36"],"short_name":"SET_UP","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/tactical.lua",119],"speed":"combat","stamina":12,"type":["cunning/tactical",3],"use_speed":"Combat"},{"cooldown":30,"cost":"30 stamina","id":"T_EXPLOIT_WEAKNESS","image":"exploit_weakness.png","info_text":"<p>Systematically find the weaknesses in your opponents\' physical resists, at the cost of 10% of your physical damage.  Each time you hit an opponent with a melee attack, you reduce their physical resistance by 5%, up to a maximum of <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">20%, 30%, 40%, 45%, 50%.</acronym></p><p></p>","mode":"sustained","multi_require":true,"name":"Exploit Weakness","points":5,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 12, Cun 36","Level 13, Cun 38","Level 14, Cun 40","Level 15, Cun 42","Level 16, Cun 44"],"short_name":"EXPLOIT_WEAKNESS","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/tactical.lua",146],"speed":"combat","sustain_stamina":30,"type":["cunning/tactical",4],"use_speed":"Combat"}],"type":"cunning/tactical"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"allow_random":true,"category":"cunning","description":"Artificer\'s tools.","name":"tools","points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"cooldown":4,"id":"T_HIDDEN_BLADES","image":"hidden_blades.png","info_text":"<p>You conceal spring loaded blades within your equipment. On scoring a critical strike, you follow up with your blades for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">145%, 164%, 178%, 190%, 201%</acronym> damage (as an unarmed attack).</p><p>This talent has a cooldown.</p><p><span style=\\"color: #ffff00\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-YELLOW\\">Prepared with: not prepared</span></span></p>","mode":"passive","name":"Hidden Blades","no_break_stealth":true,"points":1,"short_name":"HIDDEN_BLADES","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/artifice.lua",298],"type":["cunning/tools",1]},{"cooldown":8,"cost":"10 stamina","id":"T_ASSASSINATE","image":"assassinate.png","info_text":"<p>You strike your target with your Hidden Blades twice in a vital spot for 180% unarmed (physical) damage.  You must be able to see your target to use this attack, but it always hits and ignores all armor and physical resistance.</p><p>In addition, your hidden blades now inflict a further 0% of all damage dealt as bleeding over 5 turns.</p>","is_melee":true,"message":false,"mode":"activated","name":"Assassinate","points":1,"range":"melee/personal","requires_target":true,"short_name":"ASSASSINATE","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/artifice.lua",342],"stamina":10,"type":["cunning/tools",1],"use_speed":"Weapon"},{"cooldown":20,"id":"T_ROGUE_S_BREW","image":"rogue_s_brew.png","info_text":"<p>Imbibe a potent mixture of energizing and restorative substances, restoring <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">253, 328, 392, 450, 503</acronym> life, <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">63, 81, 98, 113, 127</acronym> stamina and curing <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 2, 2, 3, 3</acronym> detrimental physical effects.  The restorative effects improve with your Cunning.</p><p><span style=\\"color: #ffff00\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-YELLOW\\">Prepared with: not prepared</span></span></p>","mode":"activated","name":"Rogue\'s Brew","no_break_stealth":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","short_name":"ROGUE_S_BREW","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/artifice.lua",406],"type":["cunning/tools",1],"use_speed":"Standard"},{"id":"T_ROGUE_S_BREW_MASTERY","image":"rogue_s_brew_mastery.png","info_text":"<p>Adjust your Rogue\'s Brew formulation so that it fortifies you for 8 turns, preventing you from dying until you reach -0 life.</p>","mode":"passive","name":"Rogue\'s Brew Mastery","points":1,"short_name":"ROGUE_S_BREW_MASTERY","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/artifice.lua",485],"type":["cunning/tools",1]},{"cooldown":15,"cost":"10 stamina","direct_hit":true,"id":"T_SMOKESCREEN","image":"smokescreen.png","info_text":"<p>Throw a vial of volatile liquid that explodes in a radius 2 cloud of smoke lasting <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">4, 5, 5, 6, 6</acronym> turns.  The smoke blocks line of sight, and enemies within will have their vision range reduced by <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 4, 5, 7, 8.</acronym></p><p>Use of this talent will not break stealth, and creatures affected by the smokes can never prevent you from activating stealth, even if their proximity would normally forbid it.</p><p><span style=\\"color: #ffff00\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-YELLOW\\">Prepared with: not prepared</span></span></p>","mode":"activated","name":"Smokescreen","no_break_stealth":true,"points":1,"radius":2,"range":"6.0","requires_target":true,"short_name":"SMOKESCREEN","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/artifice.lua",499],"stamina":10,"type":["cunning/tools",1],"use_speed":"Standard"},{"id":"T_SMOKESCREEN_MASTERY","image":"smokescreen_mastery.png","info_text":"<p>You infuse your smoke bomb with chokedust. Each turn, enemies in the smoke take <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">32, 34, 37, 39, 42</acronym> nature damage and are 50% likely to be silenced.</p>","mode":"passive","name":"Smokescreen Mastery","points":1,"short_name":"SMOKESCREEN_MASTERY","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/artifice.lua",589],"type":["cunning/tools",1]},{"cooldown":10,"cost":"5 stamina","id":"T_DART_LAUNCHER","image":"dart_launcher.png","info_text":"<p>Fire a poisoned dart from a silent, concealed launcher on your person that deals <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">77, 96, 110, 122, 133</acronym> physical damage and puts the target (living only) to sleep for 4 turns, rendering them unable to act. Every <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">88, 110, 127, 141, 153</acronym> points of damage the target takes brings it closer to waking by 1 turn.</p><p>This can be used without breaking stealth.</p><p><span style=\\"color: #ffff00\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-YELLOW\\">Prepared with: not prepared</span></span></p>","mode":"activated","name":"Dart Launcher","no_break_stealth":true,"no_energy":true,"points":1,"range":"5.0","requires_target":true,"short_name":"DART_LAUNCHER","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/artifice.lua",604],"stamina":5,"type":["cunning/tools",1],"use_speed":"Instant"},{"id":"T_DART_LAUNCHER_MASTERY","image":"dart_launcher_mastery.png","info_text":"<p>The sleeping poison of your Dart Launcher becomes potent enough to ignore immunity, and upon waking the target is slowed by 7% for 4 turns.</p>","mode":"passive","name":"Dart Launcher Mastery","points":1,"short_name":"DART_LAUNCHER_MASTERY","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/artifice.lua",667],"type":["cunning/tools",1]},{"cooldown":8,"cost":"14 stamina","id":"T_GRAPPLING_HOOK","image":"grappling_hook.png","info_text":"<p>Toss out a grappling hook to a target within range <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">4, 5, 6, 7, 8.</acronym>  If this strikes either a wall or a creature that is immovable or larger than you, you will pull yourself towards it, otherwise, you will drag the target towards you.  Creatures struck by the hook will be pinned for 2 turns.</p><p>Your grapple target must be at least 2 tiles from you.</p><p><span style=\\"color: #ffff00\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-YELLOW\\">Prepared with: not prepared</span></span></p>","message":false,"mode":"activated","name":"Grappling Hook","points":1,"range":"<acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">4.6, 5.9, 6.9, 7.7, 8.4</acronym>","requires_target":true,"short_name":"GRAPPLING_HOOK","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/artifice.lua",682],"stamina":14,"type":["cunning/tools",1],"use_speed":"Standard"},{"id":"T_GRAPPLING_HOOK_MASTERY","image":"grappling_hook_mastery.png","info_text":"<p>Your grappling hook is tipped with vicious, venomous barbs. Creatures struck by it will be hit for 100% unarmed damage, bleed for <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">34, 36, 39, 42, 46</acronym> physical damage and be poisoned for <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">34, 36, 39, 42, 46</acronym> nature damage over 4 turns.</p>","mode":"passive","name":"Grappling Hook Mastery","points":1,"short_name":"GRAPPLING_HOOK_MASTERY","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/artifice.lua",808],"type":["cunning/tools",1]}],"type":"cunning/tools"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"allow_random":true,"category":"cunning","description":"The knowledge of trap laying and assorted trickeries.","name":"trapping","points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"cost":"0 stamina","id":"T_TRAP_MASTERY","image":"trap_mastery.png","info_text":"<p>This talent allows you to prepare up to <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 2, 3, 3, 3</acronym> different trap(s) of tier <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 2, 3, 4, 5</acronym> or less for later deployment. (Use this ability to select which to prepare.)</p><p>Designs known:</p><p></p><p></p><p>Traps prepared this way are difficult to detect (<acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">47, 63, 73, 82, 88</acronym> detection \'power\') and disarm (<acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">59, 79, 92, 102, 111</acronym> disarm \'power\') based on your Cunning.  They gain <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">+41%, +72%, +97%, +117%, +135%</acronym> effectiveness, and can be deployed without breaking stealth <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">70%, 86%, 98%, 100%, 100%</acronym> of the time.</p><p>You are immune to the damage and negative effects of your traps, and traps may critically strike based on your physical crit chance.</p><p>Most traps last <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">9, 11, 12, 13, 14</acronym> turns if not triggered, and refund 80% of their stamina cost on expiration.</p><p>More designs may be discovered via disarming or learned from special instructors in the world.</p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Trap Mastery","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":5,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 0, Cun 15","Level 3, Cun 17","Level 8, Cun 19","Level 15, Cun 21","Level 24, Cun 23"],"short_name":"TRAP_MASTERY","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/traps.lua",556],"stamina":0,"type":["cunning/trapping",1],"use_speed":"Standard"},{"cooldown":15,"cost":"15 stamina","id":"T_LURE","image":"lure.png","info_text":"<p>Deploy a noisy lure that attracts all creatures within radius <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">4, 6, 7, 8, 9</acronym> to it for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">6, 10, 12, 14, 16</acronym> turns.</p><p>It has <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">160, 200, 227, 248, 266</acronym> life (based on your Cunning) and is very durable, with <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">13, 19, 24, 28, 32</acronym> armor and <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">66%, 70%, 72%, 74%, 76%</acronym> resistance to non-physical damage.</p><p>At level 5, when the lure is destroyed, it will trigger some traps in a radius of 2 around it (check individual trap descriptions to see if they are triggered).</p><p>Use of this talent will not break stealth.</p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Lure","no_break_stealth":true,"points":5,"range":"<acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">3.0, 5.0, 6.0, 6.0, 7.0</acronym>","require":["Level 4, Cun 20","Level 5, Cun 22","Level 6, Cun 24","Level 7, Cun 26","Level 8, Cun 28"],"short_name":"LURE","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/traps.lua",669],"speed":"combat","stamina":15,"type":["cunning/trapping",2],"use_speed":"Combat"},{"id":"T_TRAP_LAUNCHER","image":"trap_launcher.png","info_text":"<p>You learn new techniques for setting traps.</p><p>Deploying one of your traps is possible up to 1 grids from you, takes <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">9%, 15%, 19%, 22%, 25%</acronym> less time than normal, and has <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1%, 3%, 4%, 6%, 8%</acronym> less chance to break stealth.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":true,"name":"Advanced Trap Deployment","points":5,"require":["Level 8, Cun 28","Level 9, Cun 30","Level 10, Cun 32","Level 11, Cun 34","Level 12, Cun 36"],"short_name":"TRAP_LAUNCHER","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/traps.lua",756],"type":["cunning/trapping",3]},{"cost":"0 stamina","id":"T_TRAP_PRIMING","image":"trap_priming.png","info_text":"<p>You prepare an additional trap (up to tier <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 2, 3, 4, 5</acronym>) with a special primed trigger that causes it to activate immediately when deployed. (Use this ability to select the trap.)</p><p>Not all traps can be prepared this way and each trap can have only one type of preparation.</p><p>Known primable designs:</p><p></p><p></p><p>A trap with a primed trigger gains <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">+22%, +42%, +58%, +71%, +83%</acronym> effectiveness (replacing the normal bonus from Trap Mastery) and won\'t break stealth <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">61%, 71%, 79%, 85%, 91%</acronym> of the time.</p><p><span style=\\"color: #ffff00\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-YELLOW\\">Current primed trap: none</span></span></p>","message":false,"mode":"activated","multi_require":true,"name":"Trap Priming","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":5,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 12, Cun 36","Level 13, Cun 38","Level 14, Cun 40","Level 15, Cun 42","Level 16, Cun 44"],"short_name":"TRAP_PRIMING","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/traps.lua",770],"stamina":0,"type":["cunning/trapping",4],"use_speed":"Standard"}],"type":"cunning/trapping"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"allow_random":true,"category":"cunning","description":"Collection of known traps.","name":"traps","points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"allow_primed_trigger":true,"cooldown":8,"cost":"15 stamina","id":"T_SPRINGRAZOR_TRAP","image":"springrazor_trap.png","info_text":"<p>Lay a pressure triggered trap that explodes into a radius 2 wave of razor sharp wire, doing <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">176, 216, 247, 272, 295</acronym> physical damage. Those struck by the wire may be shredded, reducing accuracy, armor and defence by <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">21, 25, 29, 32, 35.</acronym></p><p>This trap can use a primed trigger and a high level lure can trigger it.</p>","message":"@Source@ activates a prepared device.","mode":"activated","name":"Springrazor Trap","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","short_name":"SPRINGRAZOR_TRAP","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/traps.lua",857],"stamina":15,"trap_mastery_level":2,"type":["cunning/traps",1],"type_no_req":true,"use_speed":"Special"},{"allow_primed_trigger":true,"cooldown":12,"cost":"10 stamina","id":"T_BEAR_TRAP","image":"bear_trap.png","info_text":"<p>Lay a pressure triggered bear trap that snaps onto the first creature passing over it.  Victims are dealt <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">91, 106, 119, 129, 138</acronym> physical damage and become snared (pinned and slowed 30%) and wounded for <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">91, 106, 119, 129, 138</acronym> bleeding damage over 5 turns.  Creatures that avoid being snared still suffer bleeding damage.</p>","message":"@Source@ activates a prepared device.","mode":"activated","name":"Bear Trap","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","short_name":"BEAR_TRAP","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/traps.lua",937],"stamina":10,"trap_mastery_level":1,"type":["cunning/traps",1],"type_no_req":true,"use_speed":"Special"},{"cooldown":15,"cost":"25 stamina","id":"T_DISARMING_TRAP","image":"disarming_trap.png","info_text":"<p>Lay a tricky trap that maims creatures passing by with acid doing <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">222, 269, 306, 337, 364</acronym> damage and disarming them for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">2, 3, 4, 4, 5</acronym> turns.</p>","message":"@Source@ activates a prepared device.","mode":"activated","name":"Disarming Trap","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","short_name":"DISARMING_TRAP","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/traps.lua",1000],"stamina":25,"trap_mastery_level":1,"type":["cunning/traps",1],"type_no_req":true,"use_speed":"Special"},{"cooldown":20,"cost":"10 stamina","id":"T_PITFALL_TRAP","image":"pitfall_trap.png","info_text":"<p>Lay a pressure triggered trap that collapses the ground under the target, dealing <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">186, 226, 257, 282, 305</acronym> physical damage while burying them (removing from combat) for 5 turns.</p><p>Victims may resist being buried, in which case they are pinned (ignores 50% pin immunity) instead.</p>","message":"@Source@ activates a prepared device.","mode":"activated","name":"Pitfall Trap","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","short_name":"PITFALL_TRAP","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/traps.lua",1057],"stamina":10,"trap_mastery_level":3,"type":["cunning/traps",1],"type_no_req":true,"use_speed":"Special"},{"allow_primed_trigger":true,"cooldown":12,"cost":"12 stamina","id":"T_FLASH_BANG_TRAP","image":"flash_bang_trap.png","info_text":"<p>Lay a trap that explodes in a radius of 2, dealing <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">201, 241, 272, 297, 320</acronym> physical damage and blinding and dazing (50% chance of each) any creature caught inside for <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">6, 6, 7, 7, 7</acronym> turns.</p><p>This trap can use a primed trigger and a high level lure can trigger it.</p>","message":"@Source@ activates a prepared device.","mode":"activated","name":"Flash Bang Trap","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","short_name":"FLASH_BANG_TRAP","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/traps.lua",1175],"stamina":12,"trap_mastery_level":4,"type":["cunning/traps",1],"type_no_req":true,"use_speed":"Special"},{"cooldown":20,"cost":"20 stamina","id":"T_BLADESTORM_TRAP","image":"bladestorm_trap.png","info_text":"<p>Lay a trap that activates a lethal contraption of whirling blades, lasting <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">6, 8, 9, 9, 10</acronym> turns.  This stationary construct is very durable, receives your damage bonuses, and automatically attacks all adjacent enemies each turn.</p>","message":"@Source@ activates a prepared device.","mode":"activated","name":"Bladestorm Trap","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","short_name":"BLADESTORM_TRAP","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/traps.lua",1256],"stamina":20,"trap_mastery_level":5,"type":["cunning/traps",1],"type_no_req":true,"use_speed":"Special"},{"cooldown":15,"cost":"24 stamina","id":"T_BEAM_TRAP","image":"beam_trap.png","info_text":"<p>Lay a magical trap that fires a beam of arcane energy at a random foe (within range 5) each turn for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">3, 4, 5, 6, 7</acronym> turns, inflicting <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">46, 78, 102, 123, 141</acronym> arcane damage.</p><p>This trap requires 20 Magic to prepare and does not refund stamina when it expires.</p><p><span style=\\"color: #ffff00\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-YELLOW\\">Activates immediately when placed.</span></span></p>","is_spell":true,"message":"@Source@ activates a prepared device.","mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Beam Trap","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Mag 20; Talent not unlocked"],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"BEAM_TRAP","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/traps.lua",1307],"stamina":24,"trap_mastery_level":3,"type":["cunning/traps",1],"type_no_req":true,"use_speed":"Special"},{"allow_primed_trigger":true,"cooldown":10,"cost":"12 stamina","id":"T_POISON_GAS_TRAP","image":"poison_gas_trap.png","info_text":"<p>Lay a trap that releases a radius 3 cloud of thick poisonous gas lasting 4 turns.</p><p>Each turn, the cloud poisons all within (<acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">186, 226, 257, 282, 305</acronym> nature damage over 5 turns).   There is a 25% chance the poison is enhanced with crippling, numbing or insidious effects.</p><p>This trap can use a primed trigger and a high level lure can trigger it.</p>","message":"@Source@ activates a prepared device.","mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Poison Gas Trap","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Talent not unlocked"],"short_name":"POISON_GAS_TRAP","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/traps.lua",1388],"stamina":12,"trap_mastery_level":2,"type":["cunning/traps",1],"type_no_req":true,"unlock_talent":"You have learned how to create Poison Gas traps!","use_speed":"Special"},{"allow_primed_trigger":true,"cooldown":12,"cost":"12 stamina","id":"T_FREEZING_TRAP","image":"freezing_trap.png","info_text":"<p>Lay a trap that explodes into a radius 2 cloud of freezing vapour when triggered.  Foes take <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">116, 140, 158, 173, 187</acronym> cold damage and are pinned for 3 turns.</p><p>The freezing vapour persists for 5 turns, dealing <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">39, 47, 53, 58, 62</acronym> cold damage each turn to foes with a 25% chance to freeze.</p><p>This trap can use a primed trigger and a high level lure can trigger it.</p>","message":"@Source@ activates a prepared device.","mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Freezing Trap","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Talent not unlocked"],"short_name":"FREEZING_TRAP","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/traps.lua",1469],"stamina":12,"trap_mastery_level":3,"type":["cunning/traps",1],"type_no_req":true,"use_speed":"Special"},{"allow_primed_trigger":true,"cooldown":15,"cost":"15 stamina","id":"T_DRAGONSFIRE_TRAP","image":"dragonsfire_trap.png","info_text":"<p>Lay a pressure triggered trap that explodes in a radius 2 cloud of searing flames when triggered, stunning foes with the blast (<acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">46, 55, 63, 69, 74</acronym> fire damage per turn) for 3 turns.</p><p>The deflagration persists in the area for 5 turns, burning foes for <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">68, 83, 94, 103, 111</acronym> fire damage each turn.</p><p>This trap can use a primed trigger and a high level lure can trigger it.</p>","message":"@Source@ activates a prepared device.","mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Dragonsfire Trap","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Talent not unlocked"],"short_name":"DRAGONSFIRE_TRAP","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/traps.lua",1557],"stamina":15,"trap_mastery_level":5,"type":["cunning/traps",1],"type_no_req":true,"use_speed":"Special"},{"cooldown":20,"cost":"15 stamina","id":"T_GRAVITIC_TRAP","image":"gravitic_trap.png","info_text":"<p>Lay a trap that creates a radius 5 gravitic anomaly when triggered by foes approaching within range 1.  Each turn, the anomaly deals <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Magic 100\\">81, 96, 109, 119, 128</acronym> temporal damage (based on your Magic) to foes while pulling them towards its center (chance increases with your combat accuracy or spell power, whichever is higher).</p><p>Each anomaly lasts <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">3, 4, 4, 4, 5</acronym> turns (up to the amount of time since the last anomaly dissipated, based on your Trap Mastery skill).</p><p>The trap may trigger more than once, but requires at least 2 turns to recharge between activations.</p><p>This design does not require advanced preparation to use.</p>","is_spell":true,"message":"@Source@ deploys a warped device.","mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Gravitic Trap","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Talent not unlocked"],"short_name":"GRAVITIC_TRAP","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/traps.lua",1652],"stamina":15,"type":["cunning/traps",1],"type_no_req":true,"use_speed":"Special"},{"cooldown":25,"cost":"20 stamina","id":"T_AMBUSH_TRAP","image":"ambush_trap.png","info_text":"<p>Lay a magical trap that summons a trio of shadowy rogues to attack the target.</p><p>The rogues receive your damage bonuses and are permanently stealthed.</p><p>They disappear after <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">3, 4, 6, 6, 7</acronym> turns or when their work is done.</p>","is_spell":true,"message":"@Source@ activates a prepared device.","mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Ambush Trap","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Talent not unlocked"],"short_name":"AMBUSH_TRAP","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/traps.lua",1772],"stamina":20,"trap_mastery_level":5,"type":["cunning/traps",1],"type_no_req":true,"unlock_talent":"You have learned how to create Ambush traps!","use_speed":"Special"},{"allow_primed_trigger":true,"cooldown":15,"cost":"20 stamina","id":"T_PURGING_TRAP","image":"purging_trap.png","info_text":"<p>Lay a trap that releases a burst of antimagic energies (radius 2), draining up to <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Willpower 100\\">201, 241, 271, 297, 319</acronym> mana, <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Willpower 100\\">100, 120, 135, 148, 159</acronym> vim, <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Willpower 100\\">50, 60, 67, 74, 79</acronym> positive and <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Willpower 100\\">50, 60, 67, 74, 79</acronym> negative energies from affected targets, while inflicting up to <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Willpower 100\\">201, 241, 272, 297, 320</acronym> arcane damage based on the resources drained, silencing for <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">2, 3, 4, 4, 5</acronym> turns, and removing up to <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">1, 2, 2, 3, 3</acronym> beneficial magical effects or sustains.</p><p>The draining effect scales with your Willpower, and you must have 25 Willpower to prepare this trap.</p><p>This trap can use a primed trigger and a high level lure can trigger it.</p>","is_antimagic":true,"message":"@Source@ activates a prepared device.","mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Purging Trap","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Wil 25; Talent not unlocked"],"short_name":"PURGING_TRAP","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/traps.lua",1832],"stamina":20,"trap_mastery_level":4,"type":["cunning/traps",1],"type_no_req":true,"use_speed":"Special"},{"allow_primed_trigger":true,"cooldown":8,"cost":"15 stamina","id":"T_EXPLOSION_TRAP","image":"explosion_trap.png","info_text":"<p>Lay a simple yet effective trap that explodes in a radius 2 on contact, setting those affected on fire for <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">277, 333, 375, 411, 443</acronym> fire damage over 3 turns.</p><p>This trap can use a primed trigger and a high level lure can trigger it.</p>","message":"@Source@ activates a prepared device.","mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Explosion Trap","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Talent not unlocked"],"short_name":"EXPLOSION_TRAP","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/traps.lua",1961],"stamina":15,"trap_mastery_level":2,"type":["cunning/traps",1],"type_no_req":true,"unlock_talent":"You have learned how to create Explosion traps!","use_speed":"Special"},{"cooldown":10,"cost":"15 stamina","id":"T_CATAPULT_TRAP","image":"catapult_trap.png","info_text":"<p>Deploy a hidden spring-loaded catapult that will trigger (by pressure) for any creature passing over it.  Victims will be knocked back towards a target location up to <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">3, 5, 6, 7, 8</acronym> grids away and be dazed for 5 turns.</p><p>This trap has a <acronym class=\\"talent-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60\\">90%, 92%, 94%, 94%, 95%</acronym> chance to reset itself after triggering, but can only trigger once per turn.</p><p>The chance to affect the target improves with your combat accuracy.</p>","message":"@Source@ activates a prepared device.","mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Catapult Trap","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Talent not unlocked"],"short_name":"CATAPULT_TRAP","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/cunning/traps.lua",2036],"stamina":15,"trap_mastery_level":3,"type":["cunning/traps",1],"type_no_req":true,"unlock_talent":"You have learned how to create Catapult traps!","use_speed":"Special"},{"cooldown":8,"cost":"15 stamina","id":"T_NIGHTSHADE_TRAP","image":"nightshade_trap.png","info_text":"<p>Lay a trap armed with potent venom.  A creature passing over it will be dealt <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">267, 323, 365, 401, 433</acronym> nature damage and be stunned and poisoned for <acronym class=\\"variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Trap Mastery talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.60,<br>Cunning 100\\">27, 32, 37, 40, 43</acronym> nature damage per turn for 4 turns.</p>","message":"@Source@ activates a prepared device.","mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Nightshade Trap","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Talent not unlocked"],"short_name":"NIGHTSHADE_TRAP","source_code":["data/talents/cunning/traps.lua",2156],"stamina":15,"trap_mastery_level":4,"type":["cunning/traps",1],"type_no_req":true,"unlock_talent":"You have learned how to create Nightshade traps!","use_speed":"Special"}],"type":"cunning/traps"}]')}}]);